{
  "stem": "3022.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Her maiden name was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Bochner. ?] She came from the town of Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Her grandfather was a Chrzanow [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Hasidic, ?] which means the-- the pious or the [? wunderrabbi ?] of Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Despite the fact that she was very observant and very knowledgeable and gave the children a Jewish education, she also gave all her children a secular education.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My mother, besides going through religious school of [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Batheokow, ?] also attended the middle school, common school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My mother, besides speaking Hebrew, Yiddish, and Polish, studied other languages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She spoke French.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She read in those languages, French, German, and Esperanto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My father, as I said, was a butcher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the best I remember up to till the age of six, he had a small butcher shop.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Later on, in 1928, 1929, when the Depression came to Poland, he had to abandon the butcher shop, and he was helping out my grandmother and my grandfather and his wholesale fish business.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We-- my mother was a romantic, loved to read books, preferred the bucolic settings for her-- for the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she preferred to live outside what was known as the ghetto, so we always wound up living sometime in the suburbs where there were trees and-- and, you know, pastoral settings.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But I had to commute to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I went to the [NON-ENGLISH] at the age of four and five.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And later on, I went to-- to a Hebrew public school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That particular school was an annex to the Hebrew high school, which was an accredited high school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the-- the language that was taught, basically, now in the school was Polish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "However, the second language was Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the Hebrew history and Bible was subject.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was not an Orthodox school.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
